  "body": "# ðŸ¦„ Feature Tracking\r\n\r\n**Current status** (opt-in or opt-out): \r\n- `opt-in`\r\n\r\n**Opt-in feature flag name**:\r\n`--enable-sync-backtracking`\r\n\r\n**Opt-out feature flag name**: \r\n`--disable-sync-backtracking`\r\n\r\n\r\n### Feature Description\r\n\r\nTurns on backtracking routine when init-sync works on block beyond the finalized epoch (alternative branches are explored).\r\n\r\n### Tasks\r\n\r\n- [x] Feature flag created as opt-in #7564\r\n- [x] Feature implemented / code complete\r\n- [x] Feature tested in production for adequate amount of time\r\n- [x] Feature flag is inverted to be opt-out and the opt-in flag is deprecated #8034\r\n- [x] Feature has made it to a tagged production release as an opt-out flag `tag: v1.10`\r\n- [x] Opt-out feature flag is deprecated and old code paths are cleaned up #8371\r\n\r\nThis issue should be closed after all of the above tasks are complete.\r\n",
